{"tid":1121763,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"武磊：希望利物浦奪得歐聯冠軍","createTime":"2019-04-23T13:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T14:19:48.000Z","uid":19527,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"73f81aade9603e94fe2603fcaa55d7c319fe11b9","tid":1121763,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"今年冬窗，武磊加盟了愛斯賓奴隊，登陸西甲之後，武磊（W.Lei）的表現非常亮眼。日前，武磊接受了國內某媒體的採訪，他對自己喜歡的球隊等話題，發表了看法。<br />\n<br />\n　　武磊被問及自己最喜歡的球隊，結果他的答案是阿仙奴，武磊表示：「我最希望今年利物浦奪冠，去年他們很可惜沒能奪冠。我最喜歡的球隊是阿仙奴，但他們早早就遭到淘汰（註：今季阿仙奴踢歐霸盃）。」<br />\n<br />\n　　武磊還希望利物浦奪得歐聯冠軍，目前紅軍已經殺入歐聯四強，4強對手是巴塞。另外半區的4強，是熱刺對陣阿積士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190423/4/17/2/武磊-最喜歡球隊是阿仙奴-希望利物浦奪歐冠盃冠軍-10075569.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.sina.com.hk%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F20190423%2F4%2F17%2F2%2F%E6%AD%A6%E7%A3%8A-%E6%9C%80%E5%96%9C%E6%AD%A1%E7%90%83%E9%9A%8A%E6%98%AF%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%99%E5%A5%B4-%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E5%88%A9%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%A6%E5%A5%AA%E6%AD%90%E5%86%A0%E7%9B%83%E5%86%A0%E8%BB%8D-10075569.html&d=%2FIqeUsS3N0qecbTP5cC9OIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=3cf09cef\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.sina.com.hk/news/article/20190423/4/17/2/武磊-最喜歡球隊是阿仙奴-希望利物浦奪歐冠盃冠軍-10075569.html</a>"},{"pid":"e6bba0452c39e32976d741cce11b44d29db481e5","tid":1121763,"uid":114328,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"估唔到武磊d中文咁好"},{"pid":"7a233ac6eb5150cd2be8913598732ad79e5fa2ee","tid":1121763,"uid":26708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:58:53.000Z","msg":"利阿互含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />含"},{"pid":"c93bbfffd186dec752b3cfbfd9408cf212433682","tid":1121763,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"e6bba0452c39e32976d741cce11b44d29db481e5","tid":1121763,"uid":114328,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T13:58:22.000Z","msg":"估唔到武磊d中文咁好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T1